CURRENT VERSION(v1.18)
-------------------------------------------------------------

-----
/root_folder/index.php
Added instructions to handle storing client names
Reworked some code so the on show_all_contacts, you will see "Contact name(Contact@email)"


----
/root_folder/add_contacts.php
Added script to handle storing client names (mainly just added an array, and
modified the query so it would store it)

Modified the mailer to add the contacts name to the verification email


----
/root_folder/send_email.php
modified the to field to add the contacts name
modified the admin to add the mail groups name


----
/root_folder/admin/add_user.php
added group_name to the user add sql


----
/root_folder/admin/update_user.php
populated file (forgot to in last release) works now!


----
/root_folder/admin/index.php
added group_name to add_user and show_all_users. 
Changed username to read-only (no need to change users names).


----
/root_folder/installer/index.php
Added the group_name row to the users table
added the updater script, for people upgrading from the previous version (v1)


----


